Standard and Poor's Corp said itraised to BBB-plus from BBB Hechinger Co's 86 mln dlrs ofconvertible subordinated debentures of 2009.    S and P cited Hechinger's outstanding record of sales andearnings growth as well as what it termed the company'sposition as one of the best operators in the retail homeimprovement industry.    It also said the firm's financial performance as measuredby profitability and debt leverage underscore strong creditquality. S and P assigned a BBB-plus rating to Hechinger'splanned 100 mln dlr issue of convertible debt due 2012. Reuter&#3;